{"type":"CODE","files":[{"path":"index.ts","content":"export function fizzbuzz(n:number){const out=[] as string[];for(let i=1;i<=n;i++){let s=\"\";if(i%3===0)s+=\"Fizz\";if(i%5===0)s+=\"Buzz\";out.push(s||String(i))}return out}\nexport function romanToInt(s:string){const m=new Map([['I',1],['V',5],['X',10],['L',50],['C',100],['D',500],['M',1000]]);let ans=0;for(let i=0;i<s.length;i++){const v=m.get(s[i])!, nxt=m.get(s[i+1]||'')||0;ans+= v < nxt ? -v : v;}return ans;}\n"}],"language":"TYPESCRIPT","entrypoint":"index.ts"}
